#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:4
#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:25
#: twiga_power/templates/components/navbar.html:39
msgid "Qui sommes-nous ?"
msgstr "Who are we?"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:17
msgid "Directeur Général"
msgstr "Managing Director"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:27
msgid ""
"Créée en novembre 2024, Twiga Power SARL est une société de droit congolais "
"constituée sous la forme d’une Société à Responsabilité Limitée (SARL). Elle "
"s’inscrit dans une dynamique de développement énergétique visant à apporter "
"des solutions innovantes et adaptées au contexte de la République "
"Démocratique du Congo."
msgstr ""
"Created in November 2024, Twiga Power SARL is a Congolese company "
"incorporated as a Limited Liability Company (SARL). It is part of an energy "
"development dynamic aimed at providing innovative solutions adapted to the "
"context of the Democratic Republic of Congo."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:30
msgid ""
"Animée par la volonté de fournir une énergie fiable, économiquement "
"accessible et durable, Twiga Power SARL œuvre pour soutenir la croissance "
"économique et répondre efficacement aux besoins croissants en électricité, "
"tout en contribuant à l’amélioration des conditions de vie des communautés."
msgstr ""
"Driven by the desire to provide reliable, affordable and sustainable energy, "
"Twiga Power SARL works to support economic growth and effectively meet the "
"growing demand for electricity, while helping to improve living conditions "
"in communities."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:33
#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:57
#: twiga_power/templates/components/footer.html:40
#: twiga_power/templates/components/navbar.html:44
msgid "Nous contacter"
msgstr "Contact us"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:49
msgid "Notre Mission"
msgstr "Our Mission"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:51
msgid ""
"Fournir des solutions énergétiques durables et accessibles qui contribuent "
"au développement économique et social de la République Démocratique du Congo."
msgstr ""
"Provide sustainable and accessible energy solutions that contribute to the "
"economic and social development of the Democratic Republic of Congo."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:56
msgid ""
"Répondre aux besoins fondamentaux de la population en garantissant un accès "
"fiable, sécurisé et durable à l’énergie électrique."
msgstr ""
"Meet the fundamental needs of the population by guaranteeing reliable, "
"secure and sustainable access to electrical energy."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:60
msgid ""
"Contribuer de manière responsable au développement économique, social et "
"environnemental de la République Démocratique du Congo."
msgstr ""
"Contribute responsibly to the economic, social and environmental development "
"of the Democratic Republic of Congo."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:64
msgid ""
"Aller au-delà du rôle d’énergéticien en accompagnant et en sensibilisant les "
"consommateurs à une utilisation responsable de l’électricité, afin de "
"renforcer leur satisfaction."
msgstr ""
"Go beyond the role of energy provider by supporting and raising consumer "
"awareness of the responsible use of electricity, in order to increase their "
"satisfaction."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:71
msgid "Notre Vision"
msgstr "Our Vision"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:73
msgid ""
"Être une référence nationale et un acteur central de la relance énergétique "
"durable en République Démocratique du Congo"
msgstr ""
"To be a national reference and a key player in sustainable energy recovery "
"in the Democratic Republic of Congo"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:78
msgid ""
"Électrifier les zones rurales et urbaines afin de réduire les inégalités "
"d’accès à l’électricité."
msgstr ""
"Electrify rural and urban areas to reduce inequalities in access to "
"electricity."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:82
msgid ""
"Promouvoir les énergies renouvelables et l’innovation pour des solutions "
"modernes et durables."
msgstr ""
"Promote renewable energy and innovation for modern and sustainable solutions."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:86
msgid ""
"Former la main-d’œuvre locale afin de renforcer les compétences et garantir "
"un service de qualité."
msgstr ""
"Train the local workforce to strengthen skills and ensure quality service."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:100
msgid "Nos Valeurs"
msgstr "Our Values"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:102
msgid ""
"Ces valeurs guident chaque décision et chaque action de Twiga Power SARL "
"dans la construction d’un système énergétique fiable, durable et responsable."
msgstr ""
"These values guide every decision and every action of Twiga Power SARL in "
"building a reliable, sustainable and responsible energy system."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:107
msgid "Respect"
msgstr "Respect"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:109
msgid ""
"Le respect constitue le socle des relations de Twiga Power SARL avec les "
"clients, les partenaires, les communautés locales et les autorités "
"publiques. Il se traduit par la prise en compte des besoins des populations, "
"le respect des engagements contractuels et l’observation stricte du cadre "
"légal dans l’ensemble de ses activités énergétiques."
msgstr ""
"Respect forms the foundation of Twiga Power SARL's relationships with "
"customers, partners, local communities and public authorities. It is "
"reflected in taking into account the needs of the population, honouring "
"contractual commitments and strictly observing the legal framework in all "
"its energy activities."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:115
msgid "Excellence"
msgstr "Excellence"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:117
msgid ""
"L’excellence guide les pratiques opérationnelles et managériales de Twiga "
"Power SARL. Elle se traduit par l’adoption de standards techniques élevés, "
"l’amélioration continue des processus et le développement des compétences "
"humaines et technologiques."
msgstr ""
"Excellence guides the operational and managerial practices of Twiga Power "
"SARL. It is reflected in the adoption of high technical standards, the "
"continuous improvement of processes and the development of human and "
"technological skills."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:123
msgid "Sécurité"
msgstr "Safety"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:125
msgid ""
"La sécurité est une priorité absolue dans toutes nos opérations. Elle vise "
"la protection des personnes, des installations et des infrastructures "
"électriques, afin de prévenir les risques techniques, humains et "
"environnementaux liés à la production, au transport et à la distribution de "
"l’énergie électrique."
msgstr ""
"Safety is an absolute priority in all our operations. It focuses on "
"protecting people, installations and electrical infrastructure, in order to "
"prevent technical, human and environmental risks associated with the "
"production, transmission and distribution of electrical energy."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:131
msgid "Engagement social"
msgstr "Social commitment"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:133
msgid ""
"Twiga Power SARL considère l’énergie comme un levier de développement. "
"L’entreprise s’engage à accompagner les communautés, à sensibiliser les "
"consommateurs à une utilisation responsable de l’électricité et à contribuer "
"durablement au progrès social."
msgstr ""
"Twiga Power SARL considers energy to be a lever for development. The company "
"is committed to supporting communities, raising consumer awareness of the "
"responsible use of electricity and contributing sustainably to social "
"progress."

