msgid "Au coeur de la relance energétique de la RD Congo."
msgstr "At the heart of the DRC's energy recovery."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:20
msgid ""
"Découvrez comment Twiga Power transforme chaque watt en progrès et "
"opportunités pour tous"
msgstr ""
"Discover how Twiga Power transforms every watt into progress and "
"opportunities for all"

