msgid "En savoir plus"
msgstr "Learn more"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:34
msgid "L’électricité qui unit villes et villages."
msgstr "Electricity that connects cities and villages."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:37
msgid ""
"Des solutions modernes et durables pour connecter villes et villages à une "
"électricité fiable"
msgstr ""
"Modern and sustainable solutions to connect cities and villages with "
"reliable electricity"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:40
msgid "Explorer nos services"
msgstr "Explore our services"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:51
msgid "Ensemble, faisons briller l’avenir."
msgstr "Together, let's light up the future."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:54
msgid ""
"Twiga Power, partenaire engagé pour stimuler le développement économique et "
"améliorer les conditions de vie"
msgstr ""
"Twiga Power, a committed partner helping to drive economic development and "
"improve living conditions"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:80
#: twiga_power/templates/components/footer.html:37
msgid "Qui sommes nous ?"
msgstr "Who are we?"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:82
msgid ""
"Twiga Power, entreprise congolaise, assure l’importation, l’exportation, le "
"transport, la distribution et la commercialisation d’électricité, en "
"modernisant le secteur grâce à l’innovation et la durabilité."
msgstr ""
"Twiga Power, a Congolese company, is responsible for importing, exporting, "
"transmitting, distributing and marketing electricity, modernising the sector "
"through innovation and sustainability."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:85
msgid ""
"Notre mission est de rendre l’énergie fiable et accessible partout, des "
"villes aux zones reculées, en contribuant à un avenir de croissance, de "
"progrès et de bien-être pour chaque Congolais."
msgstr ""
"Our mission is to make energy reliable and accessible everywhere, from "
"cities to remote areas, contributing to a future of growth, progress and "
"well-being for every Congolese citizen."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:102
msgid "Nos services Énergétiques Intégrées."
msgstr "Our integrated energy services."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/home.html:105
msgid ""
"Nous offrons des solutions complètes pour garantir une électricité fiable, "
"durable et bénéfique pour les communautés comme pour l’environnement."
msgstr ""
"We offer comprehensive solutions to ensure electricity that is reliable, "
"sustainable and beneficial for both communities and the environment."

